Joseph McDermott (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joseph_McDermott_(actor) 0 Joseph McDermott (December 1878 – March 6, 1923), was an American actor of the silent era. He appeared in 76 films between 1912 and 1923. He died in Los Angeles, California by committing suicide.
